_sText:
gg_rush_arena_v1

Designed and created by: AudioEffect

Version: 1.0.0

Uploaded: 03.25.11

Map type: Gun Game

=========================================================================================

Installation:

Pretty straight forward.
Copy the cstrike folder from the zip folder into your "Steam/steamapps/[username]/counter-strike source" folder

It should prompt you to merge folders. Click Yes to All.

Now the map should be in your maplist when starting a game. When playing, a top down view of the map should appear in your radar. If you play with bots, it shouldn't have to create a nav mesh.

Future releases will include:
More detail, better gameplay, and a more refined nav mesh for the AI.
